<div class="bg1 text-white" style="background: #BDDCED;">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-items-center align-items-center text-center">
            <div class="col-md-6 offset-md-3  text-white">
                <h3 class="text-white mt-5">Thank you for your application. Please confirm the details below.</h3>
                <h4 class="text-white"> The loan amount that you have requested is between £5,000 and £15,000. </h4>
                <p style="font-size: 24px" class="text-white"> You would like to repay over <span id="loanDuration"> 6 <span> months </p>
                <div class="custom-checkbox col-12 mx-auto mt-3">
                   
                    <div class="error-checkbox"></div>
                    <div class="form-check form-switch">
                        <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" role="switch" id="flexSwitchCheckDefault"
                        data-parsley-required="true" data-parsley-group="block-2"
                        data-parsley-required-message="Please accept our terms and conditions" required>
                        <label class="form-check-label" for="flexSwitchCheckDefault" >Accept</label>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mt-3">
                        By clicking accept, I agree to be contacted by Get Fast Loans and Get A
                        Loan Today via SMS in regards to Loan and Claim Products.
                        By clicking continue I confirm that these details are true and accurate
                        and that I have read the <a href="https://getfast.loans/terms-and-conditions">terms and conditions</a>
                        and <a href="https://getfast.loans/privacy"> privacy policy</a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="text-center mt-5">
                        <button style="background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #ff9b00, #f57200); border: 1px solid #cc5f00; width: 45%;"id="btn-continue" type="button" class="btn btn-success btn-lg o-btn nextStep" >Continue</button>
                    </div>

                    <div class="text-center mt-5">
                        Rates from 49.7% APR to 1333% APR. Minimum Loan Length is 3 months. Maximum Loan Length is 36 months.
                        Representative Example: £1,200 borrowed for 90 days. Total amount repayable is: £1567. Interest charged is
                        0.34% per day, amounting to £367, annual interest rate of 124% (variable). Representative APR: 49.7% (variable).
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
